section.faq
  .faq__left
    h2.faq__title DeFi Vault Management &amp;&nbsp;Automation FAQ
    a.btn.btn_primary(href=process.env.LINK_CONTACT_US target="_blank")
      | Talk to Sales
  .faq__right
    ul.faq-list
      li.faq-list__item
        .faq-list__header
          span.faq-list__title What is automated vault management in&nbsp;DeFi?
          +icon('chevron')
        .faq-list__content
          p A service that automatically executes yield strategies like rebalancing and diversification using smart contracts, maximizing returns while eliminating manual effort.
      li.faq-list__item
        .faq-list__header
          span.faq-list__title Which blockchains support cross-chain vault diversification?
          +icon('chevron')
        .faq-list__content
          p Ditto supports multi-chain diversification across Ethereum, Arbitrum, Base, and other EVM networks from a single interface.
      li.faq-list__item
        .faq-list__header
          span.faq-list__title Does Ditto offer white-label vault solutions?
          +icon('chevron')
        .faq-list__content
          p Yes. We provide white-label solutions with embeddable widgets and branded dApps for enterprises and fintechs.
      li.faq-list__item
        .faq-list__header
          span.faq-list__title How does Ditto Network ensure asset security?
          +icon('chevron')
        .faq-list__content
          p Through a non-custodial architecture where users retain key control, plus $300M+ in restaked security guarantees via EigenLayer/Symbiotic for all transactions.
      li.faq-list__item
        .faq-list__header
          span.faq-list__title Are Ditto Network's vaults ERC-4626 compatible?
          +icon('chevron')
        .faq-list__content
          p Yes. Our vaults comply with ERC-4626 and ERC-7540 standards, ensuring full compatibility with DeFi wallets, dashboards, and analytics tools.
      li.faq-list__item
        .faq-list__header
          span.faq-list__title What makes Ditto different from other vault platforms?
          +icon('chevron')
        .faq-list__content
          p Ditto combines institutional-grade security ($300M+ guarantees), multi-chain support, and non-custodial architecture tailored for DeFi protocols and asset managers.
